keyMappings:
map R reload hard
map M toggleMuteTab all
map ct LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text

#map <left> previousTab
#map <right> nextTab
map ' visitPreviousTab

map <c-]> passNextKey normal
map <a-l> moveTabLeft count=99
map <a-r> moveTabRight count=99

map m Marks.activateCreateMode swap
map ` Marks.activateGotoMode swap

map yb createTab https://www.youtube.com/
map gb createTab https://www.github.com/
map cws createTab https://chromewebstore.google.com/

# Custom Searches
map s1 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=go
map s2 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=ye
map s3 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gh
map s4 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=so
map s5 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=imdb
map s6 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gi
map s7 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gm
map s8 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=translate
map s9 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=wi
"map s9 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=mdn
map s0 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=az
searchEngines:
wi: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
go: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
ye: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
gm: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google maps
az: https://www.amazon.com/s/?field-keywords=%s

gi: https://www.google.com/search?tbm=isch&q=%s Google Images
gh: https://github.com/search?q=%s GitHub
so: https://stackoverflow.com/search?q=%s StackOverflow
mdn: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/search?q=%s MDN
imdb: https://www.imdb.com/find?s=all&q=%s IMDB
translate: https://translate.google.com/?source=osdd#auto|auto|%s Google Translator

# l: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s&btnI I'm feeling lucky...
# bi: https://www.bing.com/search?q=%s Bing
